channel.title: 614 Coder, Wanted. Not A Shit Source
channel.description:
[size=12pt]Hello Moparscape [size=14pt]I know this is my first post, but I've been on this site a lot, mainly when I was first making a 525 server and getting help. Now today though I'm asking for someone with good coding experience to help me with my new 614. I have some coding backround, but would like help from professionals.
[size=10pt]I know what your thinking, its gonna be a 614 source, that I just downloaded from here, but your completely wrong. I have the source from AlphaPkz 614, which is the same for Fatality. I know that its coded pretty good now, but I want to take it to the next level and go to the top.[/size]
If interested please pm me here, or add my skype: Useof_energy. Or Msn: [email]energy_rs@hotmail.com[/email]
